args: Okay, Ranzal, I lit the fire.\nNow we're all ready forâ€”
Slow down! I got me a process here!\nFirst, we gotta put these to use...
Powder and... ARE YA KIDDIN' ME?!\nThese are herbs and spices, ya dolt!
Ya rub 'em into the seafood to\nenhance the flavor while it cooks.
Really? I always thought a barbecue\nwas just throwing things on a grill.
Well, it ain't! So take these\nseasonings and start rubbin'.
All right, everything's cooked to perfection.
Heh. Looks like my stomach thinks so, too.
Well, tell your gut sack to take five;\nwe gotta serve Cleo first.
Me and the boss man here have spent\nhours gatherin' up ingredients, and now\nwe're throwin' everybody a barbecue!
You two seriously cooked ALL that?!
AND WE GET TO EAT IT?!?!
'Course ya do! That's why we made it.
BUT...the first helpin' goes to Cleo.
'Cause yer always cookin' for us\nand we wanna pay ya back.
That isn't a favor which need be repaid.\nI am happy to do it.
Cleo, it's only right to repay people\nwho do nice things for you.
We made all this for you, Cleo,\nand it's only gettin' colder.
It's gonna break this food's little fishy\nheart what if ya don't eat it.
If this is truly so important to you,\nthen I gratefully accept.
I will be honest, Ranzalâ€”I did not\nexpect much from your cooking.
But this has been flawlessly prepared,\nand is grilled to perfection.

I always cooked for myself back in my
solo merc days, so I realized pretty quick
that I had to get better unless I wanted
to be snackin' on ash all day.
Took some trial and error,\nbut I mostly figured it out.
I can't believe you achieved this level\nof skill through experimentation alone.
All right, Cleo's filled up her plate,\nso the rest of ya lumps, get in there!
I'm gonna eat until I pukeâ€”and then I'll\nuse all the extra room to eat MORE!
Whoa, stop pushin' already! We got\nenough food here for a damn army.
Oh man, this crab is as good as it looks!
And this Lord of the Sea fillet\nis simply succulent!
I have never tasted a mushroom like this.\nIt has an almost...mystical quality.
Looks like everyone's enjoyin' the grub.
Gathering the ingredients wasn't easy,\nbut this makes it all worthwhile.
Maybe we oughta make it a point\nto do stuff like this from time to time.
Are you two gonna eat or what?\nBecause I am totally going to horf down\nyour share if you keep standing there!
Guess we better grab a plate, eh, boss?
